26:54.544 --> 26:55.926
It's sort of like cotton candy.

26:55.986 --> 26:57.969
Remember the first time you ever ate cotton candy?

26:58.250 --> 26:58.830
Man, I do.

26:59.151 --> 27:01.234
As a little kid, I saw that giant

27:01.666 --> 27:02.728
cotton candy thing.

27:02.788 --> 27:07.276
I thought, this is going to take me a week, but I am going to eat through this whole cotton candy.

27:07.296 --> 27:10.661
It took me about five seconds because you put it in your mouth.

27:10.681 --> 27:11.323
It just melts.

27:11.383 --> 27:16.632
It's just a little bit of sugar that's turned into this big thing.

27:16.672 --> 27:22.642
And all grace and no truth is sort of like cotton candy.

27:24.450 --> 27:30.758
No, God never intended for us to be all truth and no grace and all are all grace and no truth.

27:30.778 --> 27:39.350
He intended us to be full of grace and full of truth at the same time.

27:40.431 --> 27:43.014
Two months ago, we had Hurricane Burl.

27:43.395 --> 27:44.256
We didn't expect to.

27:44.897 --> 27:48.882
All of the predictions was that it was going to go far

27:48.994 --> 27:51.537
to the west of Houston.

27:51.798 --> 27:57.485
And then in the last day or two, I don't remember exactly how long of notice we got it changed course.

27:58.026 --> 28:00.329
And the eye of the hurricane came over us.

28:03.433 --> 28:07.579
And did you know that as soon as that change happened, it was all over the news.

28:07.679 --> 28:12.565
I mean, everywhere you go, I remember we got burl that's gonna hit us in a day or two or whatever it was.

28:13.026 --> 28:16.210
And it was everywhere you went, burls coming, burls coming.

28:17.474 --> 28:21.600
And I want to tell you, I think all these people that did that just obviously didn't love us.

28:23.483 --> 28:24.104
They didn't love us.

28:24.685 --> 28:29.112
If they would have loved us, they would have said, you know, let's don't ruin the day.

28:29.152 --> 28:35.321
Yeah, I know that it's not, it's going to come like on whatever day.

28:35.962 --> 28:37.524
I remember that Monday was at Monday.

28:37.545 --> 28:40.489
I don't know when it was, but let's don't ruin Sunday.

28:41.330 --> 28:41.951
They're happy.

28:41.991 --> 28:43.794
Let's let them stay happy.

28:44.386 --> 28:46.889
Why give them misery for Sunday?

28:46.929 --> 28:52.056
They'll wake up on Monday, it won't be so good, but at least they had a good Sunday.

28:54.840 --> 28:55.180
Oh no.

28:56.602 --> 29:05.634
Instead, they told us a day or two in advance and they did it because they wanted us to know the truth and they wanted us to get ready.

29:08.738 --> 29:11.762
And the reality is that actually was real love.

29:15.522 --> 29:22.350
If a church truly cares about others, it'll be truthful about sin and judgment.

29:22.370 --> 29:26.415
And it'll be gracious to meet others' needs as it shares Christ.

29:27.677 --> 29:29.379
It isn't one or the other, it's both and.

29:33.744 --> 29:45.138
The Bible teaches that the lifestyle, the gay and lesbian and lifestyle, is wrought with misreadicom and is not what God intended.

29:46.402 --> 29:48.345
It warns people don't go that direction.

29:51.249 --> 29:52.271
And we want to be honest.

29:55.015 --> 30:01.665
We don't want to be the mean people that are so mean to individuals that are in this lifestyle.

30:01.685 --> 30:05.050
We want to be loving and kind, but we want to be truthful.

30:10.178 --> 30:12.621
The Bible teaches that there are two genders.

30:12.862 --> 30:13.943
It is male and female.

30:13.963 --> 30:15.826
And by the way, science teaches that too.

30:18.562 --> 30:20.244
It's not exclusive to the Bible.

30:21.185 --> 30:29.474
Richard Dawkins is a well-known guy, a scientist, because of his atheism, and he's just well-known.

30:29.935 --> 30:41.347
And Richard Dawkins, I read an article that he wrote about this, and he said this whole thing of three or 30 genders, whatever the number is now, he said, this is all fantasy.

30:43.109 --> 30:44.190
It's all made up.

30:44.270 --> 30:45.291
It's all made believe.

30:45.311 --> 30:46.012
It's not true.

30:46.052 --> 30:47.634
There's two genders, he said.

30:48.098 --> 30:50.861
male and female, that science.

30:51.502 --> 30:57.509
And then he went on to say that scientists who are capitulating to this are only doing it because they want their funding.

31:04.617 --> 31:10.163
I'm here to tell you that I don't understand transgenderism and I'm being upfront about that and I've said that to you before.

31:10.303 --> 31:11.704
I don't, I don't understand it.

31:12.165 --> 31:16.690
I do know that all through decades and decades, about half a percent

31:18.402 --> 31:23.909
and I don't understand it, and I want a better understanding than I do.

31:23.929 --> 31:26.012
But today, it's like six or seven percent.

31:26.132 --> 31:34.183
So how in the world, all these decades and decades, it's been a half percent, and suddenly in just this generation, just right now, it's turned out to be seven percent.

31:34.223 --> 31:34.884
How did that happen?

31:36.145 --> 31:45.938
It's called recruitment, and it's taking advantage of especially teenage girls as it's turning out.

31:50.402 --> 31:51.323
but there's two genders.

31:54.627 --> 32:00.013
We want to be people of the truth and we want to be people of grace.

32:03.316 --> 32:06.840
Second of all, what we believe really does matter.

32:09.383 --> 32:19.154
Jesus said about this church, you have love and faith and dedication, persistence,

32:20.514 --> 32:22.297
But he says, here's what I have against you.

32:22.577 --> 32:26.823
In the name of tolerance, you have given up truth.

32:28.546 --> 32:31.069
I've had people that have said to me, look, I don't want doctrine.

32:32.471 --> 32:33.353
I don't want doctrine.

32:33.593 --> 32:35.957
Just tell me how the Bible can improve my life.

32:38.320 --> 32:41.485
And I think to myself, okay, I understand, they don't understand.

32:41.545 --> 32:44.369
Doctrine is Bible truth.

32:46.211 --> 32:47.954
And the truth is what sets you free.

32:48.578 --> 32:50.621
That Bible truth will change your life.

32:54.266 --> 32:55.388
And I know they don't understand.

32:56.670 --> 33:06.485
But here's what Isaiah 66 verse two says, this is the one I esteem, a person who is humble and contrite in spirit who trembles at my word.

33:06.685 --> 33:08.808
And the word tremble simply means respect.

33:11.192 --> 33:13.996
It matters what we believe.

33:14.016 --> 33:18.162
Third, every teacher in our church, including Mark Hartman,

33:18.498 --> 33:24.969
is to be judged in accordance to the faithfulness to God's word, every teacher.

33:26.391 --> 33:32.962
In Revelation 2.20, he says, I am upset because you tolerate false doctrine.

33:34.564 --> 33:37.970
And you don't want to call it out because you don't want to rock the boat.

33:39.074 --> 33:45.202
Do you remember Paul why he loved the church of Berea so much in Acts 17, verse 11?

33:45.403 --> 33:51.631
And the people of Berea were more open-minded than those of Thessalonica, and they listened eagerly to Paul's message.

33:51.651 --> 33:58.360
They searched the scriptures day after day to see if what Paul and Silas were teaching was true.

34:00.583 --> 34:08.754
And if Paul needs to be checked about what he's teaching, then Mark Hartman needs to be checked.

34:09.730 --> 34:10.671
and every other teacher.

34:12.033 --> 34:13.936
Are we teaching what the Bible says?

34:14.917 --> 34:17.020
Are we teaching the Word of God?

34:17.701 --> 34:18.642
And here's the last thing.

34:19.283 --> 34:23.028
Jesus is the ultimate judge of our church.

34:24.690 --> 34:28.035
Revelation 2, 18, to the angel of the church at Thyatira, right?

34:28.075 --> 34:37.067
These are the words of the Son of God whose eyes are like blazing fire and whose feet are like burnished bronze.

34:37.948 --> 34:39.250
Jesus is saying,

34:39.330 --> 34:40.812
the Son of God, listen to me.

34:41.112 --> 34:54.188
And the eyes that is like fire just simply means that He has the ability to look through all of our excuses and all of our words and see the truth about our heart.

34:56.591 --> 35:00.115
He knows the truth and He is the judge.

35:00.195 --> 35:03.780
It's a statement of judgment that He has given in the verse.

35:05.622 --> 35:09.106
Jesus said in John chapter 12 verse 48, He that rejects me

35:09.506 --> 35:13.450
and receives not my words has one that judges him.

35:14.451 --> 35:19.437
The word that I have spoken, the same will judge him in the last day.

35:21.959 --> 35:39.378
One day I'm gonna be judged by Jesus and his word of my life and how I lived my life, but also about my ministry and how I led and what I taught.

35:40.546 --> 35:42.149
I'm gonna be held accountable for it.

35:44.192 --> 35:52.786
And one day you are going to be held accountable before Jesus, in accordance to His Word.

35:56.833 --> 36:01.180
We need to live our lives in such a way that recognizes that truth.

36:03.284 --> 36:04.325
I have one more thing to say.

36:05.728 --> 36:07.090
Jesus gives us a promise.

36:07.170 --> 36:08.393
and notice what the promise is.

36:08.473 --> 36:14.125
Revelation chapter 2 verse 25, only hold on to what you have until I come.

36:15.167 --> 36:20.418
To him who overcomes and does my will to the end, I will give authority over the nations.

36:21.220 --> 36:23.044
He will rule them with an iron scepter.

36:23.084 --> 36:27.794
He'll dash them to pieces like pottery, just as I have received authority from my father.

36:27.938 --> 36:29.940
And I will give him the morning star.

36:30.301 --> 36:33.584
He who has an ear, let him hear what the Spirit says to the churches.

36:34.085 --> 36:38.870
I don't begin to tell you that I understand everything that he just said.

36:39.231 --> 36:44.036
And we don't have time anyway this morning to look at it, but this I do understand.

36:44.336 --> 36:48.842
He says, hold on to the Word of God and the power of the Holy Spirit.

36:48.862 --> 36:49.943
Hang on to the truth.

36:51.264 --> 36:53.267
Hang on to truth, hang on to grace.

36:54.848 --> 36:56.370
And live this way.

36:56.834 --> 37:05.843
in your life, we choose to be a church with an unwavering commitment to the Word of God.

37:07.184 --> 37:07.504
Amen?

37:09.126 --> 37:09.446
Amen.

37:13.970 --> 37:26.482
Let's be the church that knows what grace is and that is kind and loving and gracious and helpful and welcoming.

37:26.690 --> 37:34.363
and let's be a church that lives by the truth of God's word because we can do, must do, both.

37:35.565 --> 37:36.025
Let's pray.

37:36.406 --> 37:40.072
Father, we come to you today and we thank you for the truth of your word.

37:40.393 --> 37:51.952
It's hard, sometimes harsh, sometimes difficult, and it cuts to the quick in the culture.

37:52.613 --> 37:53.394
It always will.

37:57.314 --> 38:09.111
God help us to be willing to even suffer for your namesake if that's what it means.

38:13.217 --> 38:25.554
But to love you and hold true to your word, we ask Father that this be who we are at Sugar Creek Baptist Church.

38:28.546 --> 38:30.528
Lord, I pray for those in this room today.

38:30.569 --> 38:32.191
This is a tough message to hear.

38:33.072 --> 38:34.614
This is a difficult thing to hear.

38:35.114 --> 38:43.805
But I pray for those in this room who have never given their heart to Christ that somehow your spirit is at work in their heart and drawing them to yourself.

38:43.825 --> 38:46.629
And this would be the day of salvation in their own heart.

38:48.451 --> 38:53.938
And I pray, God, that you would move in hearts a day to yield to you.

38:55.600 --> 38:57.202
And I pray this in Jesus' name.

38:58.210 --> 39:00.274
Amen.

